        "auditory": "I hear a sudden rise in volume—raw, forceful shouting that arrives faster than context. Words slam into each other, powered more by breath and pressure than clarity.",
        "tactile": "I sense a tense, vibrating stillness in someone's posture—like a coiled spring you can feel in the air."
    },
